claim.claim-text:
4. The method according to claim 1, further comprising:
receiving, by the eNB, a Switching Request message from a destination MME;
transmitting, by the eNB, an Answer To Switching Request message to the destination MME;
receiving, by the eNB, a Switching Completed message from the UE; and
transmitting, by the eNB, a Switching Notification message to the destination MME.
